snippet.title: Super Seymour Saves The Planet On The ZX Spectrum
snippet.description:
Swainy reviews the budget game Super Seymour Saves The Planet, which was the second Seymour game to be released by Codemasters.

Website: http://www.retroasylum.com
Podcast via iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/gb/podcast/retro-asylum-podcast/id474414834?mt=2
Podcast via Podomatic: http://retroasylum.podomatic.com/
Twitter: @RetroAsylum1
